Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.structures.structurearchetypes

@NonNullByDefault package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.structures.structurearchetypes
Contains interfaces for structures that define certain archetypes of structures.

For example, all structures that can move perpetually should implement IPerpetualMover, so the project can handle animations of such structures accordingly.
